\verb'    '弄岗喀斯特季节性雨林15公顷样地位于我国华南广西弄岗国家级自然保护区内(22.43°N，106.95°E)，是中国森林生物多样性监测网络的大型动态样地之一。弄岗大样地森林生态系统完整、地球化学背景特殊、异质性生境分化强烈，是世界少有的理想的喀斯特森林生态系统与生物多样性研究基地。\\
\verb'    'Longgang 15-ha Karst seasonal rain forest plot is located in the Longgang National Nature Reserve of the Guangxi Province, southern China (22.43°N,106.95°E).This plot is one of the large-scale forest dynamics plots of Chinese Forest Biodiversity Monitoring Network  (CForBio). This plot contains a comprehensive foest ecosystem,is characterized by special geochemical background and high differentiation in heterogeneous microhabitats, and  is an unusual and ideal study base to investigate the karst forest ecosystems and biodiversity
 in the world. }\par}
