\textbf{已开展项目} 
\begin{itemize}
\item 2010年，使用全站仪将样地划分为1500个10m×10m小样方，记录每个样点的海拔。
\item 2011年，样地内所有胸径≥1cm木本植物被挂牌，并记录物种名称、胸径、坐标、生长状态等；每5年复查一次。   
\item 2012年4月，架设90个种子雨收集器 (71cm×71cm)，植物种子和凋落物每星期收集一次；设置90×5个幼苗框 (1m×1m 或 2m×2m)，每4个月调查一次。
\item 2012年8月，样地周围布设35台红外相机，监测动物活动。
\end{itemize}
\textbf{Ongoing projects} 
\begin{itemize}
\item In 2010,the total plot had been grided into 1500 10m×10m subplots and the elevation of every subplot was recorded.
\item In 2011, all individuals with the stems ≥1 cm DBH in the plot were tagged, identified by species name,DBH,coordinate and growing status, and  re-censused by every 5 years.    
\item In April 2012, 90 seed traps (71cm×71cm) were built and seed rain and litterfall were investigated every week. 90×5 seedling subplots (1m×1m or 2m×2m) were set up around the seed traps and were surveyed every four months. 
\item In August 2012, 35 infrared cameras were set up around the plot in order to monitor animal activity.
\end{itemize}
\par}}
